000012B6                           547  ; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
000012B6                           548  BTNPLOT
000012B6                           549  ; PLOTS THE BUTTON. A RECTANGLE IS DRAWN WITH THICKNESS BTNPENWD. THE CONTOUR
